   "end": "6.520", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.960", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.680", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.280", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beitr\u00e4ge nach Leistungsf\u00e4higkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.560", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leistungen nach Bedarf: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.080", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist der Grundsatz der Finanzarchitektur in der gesetzlichen Krankenkasse. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.560", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anders als in der Rentenkasse richtet sich die Leistung der gesetzlichen Krankenkasse nicht nach der H\u00f6he der eingezahlten Beitr\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.440", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern prinzipiell nach den Ma\u00dfst\u00e4ben des Sozialgesetzbuches: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.240", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "notwendig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.080", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zweckm\u00e4\u00dfig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.800", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ausreichend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.920", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wirtschaftlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.320", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darauf hat der Versicherte ein einklagbares Recht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die H\u00f6he der Beitr\u00e4ge folgt der Leistungskraft der Versicherten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.440", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das unterscheidet die gesetzliche Krankenkasse prinzipiell von der privaten Krankenversicherung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.280", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ihre Pr\u00e4mien versicherungsmathematisch kalkulieren muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.360", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit es in der gesetzlichen Krankenkasse dennoch in einem gewissen Rahmen beim \u00c4quivalenzprinzip der Versicherung bleibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.600", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gibt es eine Beitragsbemessungsgrenze; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.440", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn wenn Steuern in die gesetzliche Krankenkasse flie\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.520", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann explizit und offen aus Haushaltsmitteln und nicht als steuer\u00e4hnliche Belastung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.040", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die man zu kaschierten Versicherungsbeitr\u00e4gen umlackiert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.920", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2015 haben wir von der Linken einen in der Semantik \u00e4hnlich lautenden Antrag vorgelegt bekommen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.000", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dem sich der Ausschuss f\u00fcr Gesundheit im Januar\u00a02016 in einer \u00f6ffentlichen Anh\u00f6rung ausf\u00fchrlich befasst hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.240", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im damaligen Antrag wie im heutigen Antrag werben Sie daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.280", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "alle Einkommensarten zur Finanzierung der gesetzlichen Kranken- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Pflegeversicherung heranzuziehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.160", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Beitragsbemessungsgrenze aufzuheben und eine, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.560", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie es nennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.720", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "solidarische Gesundheitsversicherung einzuf\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.960", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "K\u00f6nnen Sie uns bitte einmal erkl\u00e4ren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.840", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum Sie dann die Tatsache, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.960", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass gerade unterschiedliche Einkommensarten zur Finanzierung der gesetzlichen Kranken- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.240", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
