   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.600", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich erinnere an die vorhin erw\u00e4hnte Anh\u00f6rung und an das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.000", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was der Sachverst\u00e4ndige Professor Dr.\u00a0Klaus Jacobs vom Wissenschaftlichen Institut der AOK dort ausgef\u00fchrt hat:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.360", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum Zeitpunkt der Verbeitragung ist die \u00f6konomische Leistungsf\u00e4higkeit relevant. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.560", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es kommt nicht darauf an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.720", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
