   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.240", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssten wir den Gro\u00dfteil der gesetzlichen Renten beitragsfrei stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.160", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das h\u00e4tte eklatante Konsequenzen f\u00fcr die Finanzlage der gesetzlichen Krankenversicherung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.240", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Dimension dieser Konsequenzen ist in der vergangenen Legislaturperiode deutlich geworden; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.400", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn der Sachverst\u00e4ndige Dr.\u00a0Reinhold Thiede von der Deutschen Rentenversicherung Bund hat sie uns vor Augen gef\u00fchrt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.880", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
