  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.040", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber bitte in der Ansparphase. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.480", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einmal ist genug. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.320", 
   "id": "s000091", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnen den Menschen nicht erkl\u00e4ren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.360", 
   "id": "s000092", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie von ihrem eigenen Ersparten dann auch noch doppelt oder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.720", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es aus Nettoeinkommen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.880", 
   "id": "s000094", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sogar dreifach Krankenversicherungsbeitr\u00e4ge zahlen sollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.760", 
   "id": "s000095", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann ist n\u00e4mlich der Gedanke der Vorsorge und der betrieblichen Altersvorsorge perdu."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.840", 
   "id": "s000096", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da m\u00f6chte ich gerne wissen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.840", 
   "id": "s000097", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie das den Betroffenen oben auf der Besuchertrib\u00fcne erkl\u00e4ren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.720", 
   "id": "s000098", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.840", 
   "id": "s000099", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank f\u00fcr Ihre Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.320", 
   "id": "s000100", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lieber Herr Kollege. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.120", 
   "id": "s000101", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich beziehe mich einmal auf Ihren Antrag und zitiere daraus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.600", 
   "id": "s000102", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie schreiben:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.920", 
   "id": "s000103", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Doppelverbeitragung ist auch in finanzieller Hinsicht keineswegs alternativlos. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.720", 
   "id": "s000104", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eventuelle Einnahmeverluste durch die Aufhebung des"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.560", 
   "id": "s000105", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0wie Sie es nennen\u00a0\u2013"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "303.600", 
   "id": "s000106", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ungerechten doppelten Beitrags f\u00fcr Bezieherinnen und Bezieher von Betriebsrenten w\u00e4ren leicht auszugleichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "303.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "307.520", 
   "id": "s000107", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn alle Einkommensarten zur Finanzierung der gesetzlichen Kranken- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "307.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.920", 
   "id": "s000108", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Pflegeversicherung herangezogen w\u00fcrden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "316.000", 
   "id": "s000109", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Beitragsbemessungsgrenze aufgehoben und eine solidarische Gesundheitsversicherung eingef\u00fchrt werden w\u00fcrde."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.360", 
   "id": "s000110", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wenn doch alle Einkommensarten zur Finanzierung der gesetzlichen Kranken- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "322.800", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Pflegeversicherung heranzuziehen sind: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "322.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "325.160", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Woher kommt denn dann die Logik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "325.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "330.000", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ausgerechnet diese Einkommensart von der Verbeitragung auszunehmen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "330.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "332.800", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da machen Sie einen populistischen Widerspruch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "332.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "335.040", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dem Sie nichts anderes erreichen wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "335.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "340.800", 
   "id": "s000116", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als den Unmut der Betroffenen auf Ihre M\u00fchlen zu lenken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "340.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "341.880", 
   "id": "s000117", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist der Zweck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "341.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "344.280", 
   "id": "s000118", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weswegen Sie das so formulieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "344.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "348.520", 
   "id": "s000119", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist konsequent inkonsequent und v\u00f6llig widerspr\u00fcchlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "348.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "350.040", 
   "id": "s000120", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wegen der Dimension, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "350.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "353.600", 
   "id": "s000121", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die das au\u00dferdem f\u00fcr die gesetzliche Rentenkasse h\u00e4tte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "353.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "355.920", 
   "id": "s000122", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "will ich noch einmal daran erinnern: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "355.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "357.920", 
   "id": "s000123", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir hatten in 2014\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "357.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "361.960", 
   "id": "s000124", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so Reinhold Thiede in der Anh\u00f6rung vor dem Gesundheitsausschuss\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "361.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "368.920", 
   "id": "s000125", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Krankenversicherung der Rentner Ausgaben der gesetzlichen Rentenversicherung in H\u00f6he von etwa 16\u00a0Milliarden Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "368.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "372.840", 
   "id": "s000126", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist allerdings nur der Beitragsanteil der gesetzlichen Rentenversicherung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "372.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "377.400", 
   "id": "s000127", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den gleichen Anteil plus den Zusatzbeitrag tragen die Rentner. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "377.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "383.560", 
   "id": "s000128", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht also insgesamt um eine Gr\u00f6\u00dfenordnung von 30 bis 40\u00a0Milliarden Euro."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "383.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "387.200", 
   "id": "s000129", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es war das Rentenanpassungsgesetz aus dem Jahr\u00a01982, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "387.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "393.880", 
   "id": "s000130", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch das erstmals der Rente vergleichbare Einnahmen zur Beitragszahlung in der GKV herangezogen wurden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "393.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "399.240", 
   "id": "s000131", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2003 wurden die Beitragspflichten pr\u00e4zisiert und ausgeweitet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "399.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "402.520", 
   "id": "s000132", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Seitdem gibt es dar\u00fcber eine juristische Auseinandersetzung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "402.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "405.280", 
   "id": "s000133", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allerdings muss man auch darauf hinweisen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "405.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "410.880", 
   "id": "s000134", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Bundesverfassungsgericht in dieser juristischen Auseinandersetzung klargestellt hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "410.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "414.160", 
   "id": "s000135", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Gesetzgeber von Verfassungs wegen berechtigt ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "414.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "425.440", 
   "id": "s000136", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "j\u00fcngere Krankenversicherte von der Finanzierung des h\u00f6heren Aufwands f\u00fcr die Rentner zu entlasten und die Rentner entsprechend ihrem Einkommen verst\u00e4rkt zur Finanzierung heranzuziehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "425.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "430.320", 
   "id": "s000137", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist vom Bundesverfassungsgericht durchdekliniert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "430.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "433.440", 
   "id": "s000138", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich haben wir vieles unternommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "433.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "436.720", 
   "id": "s000139", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben die Attraktivit\u00e4t der Altersvorsorge gesteigert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "436.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "448.400", 
   "id": "s000140", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem wir das Recht auf Entgeltumwandlung bis zu 4\u00a0Prozent der Beitragsbemessungsgrenze der gesetzlichen Rentenversicherung zur Finanzierung einer Altersvorsorge beitragsfrei lassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "448.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "453.960", 
   "id": "s000141", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben durch das Betriebsrentenst\u00e4rkungsgesetz diese Regelung ab 2019 f\u00fcr neue Vertr\u00e4ge bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "453.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "457.960", 
   "id": "s000142", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2022 f\u00fcr bestehende Vertr\u00e4ge noch einmal gest\u00e4rkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "457.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "467.480", 
   "id": "s000143", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sodass Arbeitgeber die dadurch eingesparten Sozialversicherungsbeitr\u00e4ge in pauschalierter Form von 15\u00a0Prozent in die betriebliche Altersvorsorge zahlen m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "467.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "469.080", 
   "id": "s000144", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dar\u00fcber hinaus haben wir\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "469.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "470.560", 
   "id": "s000145", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "davon war schon die Rede\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "470.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "476.240", 
   "id": "s000146", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch das Gesetz GKV-Beitr\u00e4ge auf betriebliche Riester-Renten in der Auszahlungsphase abgeschafft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "476.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "481.080", 
   "id": "s000147", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie werden damit wie private Riester-Renten behandelt und von Beitr\u00e4gen verschont."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "481.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "484.800", 
   "id": "s000148", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sicherlich kann man \u00fcber weitere Reformen nachdenken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "484.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "489.400", 
   "id": "s000149", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann muss man aber auch einen ehrlichen Blick auf die finanziellen Konsequenzen werfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "489.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "491.800", 
   "id": "s000150", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Je nach Umfang der Vorschl\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "491.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "493.680", 
   "id": "s000151", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die realisiert werden sollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "493.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "503.120", 
   "id": "s000152", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "handelt es sich dann um eine Minderung der Finanzkraft der gesetzlichen Krankenkassen zwischen 2,6\u00a0Milliarden Euro und \u00fcber 5\u00a0Milliarden Euro."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "503.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "505.560", 
   "id": "s000153", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ohne Kompensation hie\u00dfe das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "505.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "514.240", 
   "id": "s000154", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es zu einer Erh\u00f6hung des Beitrags f\u00fcr die gesamte Solidargemeinschaft und damit auch zu einer Mehrbelastung von Geringverdienern kommt"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "514.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "518.600", 
   "id": "s000155", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder zu einer Einschr\u00e4nkung der Leistungen in der gesetzlichen Krankenkasse."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "518.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "521.880", 
   "id": "s000156", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen bitte ich Sie herzlich um Verst\u00e4ndnis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "521.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "525.520", 
   "id": "s000157", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir auf der Grundlage Ihres widerspr\u00fcchlichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "525.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "528.240", 
   "id": "s000158", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "inkonsistenten und inkonsequenten Antrags, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "528.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "532.960", 
   "id": "s000159", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der rein populistisch motiviert ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "532.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "536.280", 
   "id": "s000160", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weder das eine noch das andere \u00fcbers Knie brechen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "536.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "540.120", 
   "id": "s000161", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bedanke mich f\u00fcr Ihre Aufmerksamkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "540.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "547.000", 
   "id": "s000162", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die SPD-Fraktion spricht jetzt die Kollegin Sabine Dittmar."
   ]
  }
 ]
}